## Example 2 â€” Factor by Grouping

Factor:

`14ax^2 - 16by + 20cy + 28bx^2 - 35cx^2 - 8ay`

Group terms:

`(14ax^2 + 28bx^2 - 35cx^2) + (-8ay - 16by + 20cy)`

Factor each group:

`= 7x^2(2a + 4b - 5c) - 4y(2a + 4b - 5c)`

Factor the common binomial:

`= (7x^2 - 4y)(2a + 4b - 5c)`

